pageContext.claim: “AOC, that's a real beauty. You only have 11 years to live, folks, 11 years, because climate change is just coming up ... You know, it's 12 years, but today, I heard one of these crazies say it's down to 11, and they arrested Jane Fonda. Nothing changes.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump is oversimplifying. Some scientists say some effects from climate change may be irreversible in 11 years, not that life on Earth will soon end.
